name: Cecilia Alcott from Infinite Stratos
description:
From the anime Infinite Stratos

Might as well share it here for archive purposes

Rec Weight : 0.6-0.8

For realistic and semi realistic i suggest 0.8

Images were generated at 512x768

I also use Hires.fix for all the generated image

for optimal result uses these trigger prompt

Trigger prompt for Uniform: ceciliasomakj,school uniform,large breast

Trigger prompts for Pilot suit(without the mech): ceciliasomakj,blonde hair,leotard,blue leotard,pilot suit,large breast

add blonde hair if the hair came off differently

For non-commercial use

Image trained using mainly anime snapshot, light novel cover, some booru stuff, .All credit goes to char creator Izuru Yumizuru with illustrations by Okiura

Can't guarantee you got the same result from my prompt, could be a different upscaler/vae or clip skip.
